sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NotebookCtrl as Notebook Controller
    participant Notebook as Jupyter Notebook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS OAuth
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Tekton as Tekton Pipeline<br/>Kubernetes API
    participant KServeCtrl as KServe Controller
    participant ModelCtrl as Model Controller
    participant Knative as Knative Serving
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP mTLS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 1: Model Development to Deployment

    User->>Dashboard: 1. Create notebook workspace<br/>OAuth authentication
    Dashboard->>NotebookCtrl: 2. Create Notebook CR<br/>Kubernetes API
    NotebookCtrl->>Notebook: 3. Provision pod + OAuth proxy<br/>OpenShift Route
    Notebook-->>User: 4. JupyterLab UI ready

    User->>Notebook: 5. Develop model, train, save
    Notebook->>S3: 6. Upload model artifacts<br/>AWS S3 API, IAM auth
    S3-->>Notebook: 7. Model saved

    User->>Notebook: 8. Create pipeline (Elyra)
    Notebook->>DSP: 9. Submit pipeline<br/>KFP API
    DSP->>Tekton: 10. Create PipelineRun CR<br/>Tekton API
    Tekton->>S3: 11. Store artifacts
    Tekton-->>DSP: 12. Pipeline complete

    User->>Dashboard: 13. Create InferenceService CR
    Dashboard->>KServeCtrl: 14. InferenceService created<br/>serving.kserve.io API
    KServeCtrl->>Knative: 15. Create Knative Service<br/>Serverless autoscaling

    par Model Controller Actions
        Dashboard->>ModelCtrl: InferenceService created
        ModelCtrl->>Istio: 16a. Create VirtualService<br/>Traffic routing
        ModelCtrl->>Istio: 16b. Create PeerAuthentication<br/>mTLS PERMISSIVE
        ModelCtrl->>Prometheus: 16c. Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Metrics collection
    end

    Knative->>Predictor: 17. Create predictor pod<br/>Storage initializer
    Predictor->>S3: 18. Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS, AWS IAM
    S3-->>Predictor: 19. Model loaded
    Predictor-->>User: 20. Inference endpoint ready

    Note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 2: Inference Request Flow

    User->>Istio: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Istio->>Knative: Route to Knative Service<br/>mTLS

    alt Pod scaled to zero
        Knative->>Predictor: Scale up pod (Activator)
    end

    Knative->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>8080/TCP mTLS
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run inference
    Predictor-->>Knative: Prediction result<br/>JSON response
    Knative-->>Istio: Response
    Istio-->>User: 200 OK, prediction

    par Monitoring
        Predictor->>Prometheus: Push metrics<br/>inference_requests_total
        Prometheus->>Dashboard: Query metrics<br/>Prometheus API
        Dashboard-->>User: Display model performance
    end

    Note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 3: Distributed Training with Ray

    User->>Notebook: Submit RayCluster CR
    Notebook->>KubeRayOp as KubeRay Operator: Create RayCluster<br/>ray.io API

    opt CodeFlare Queueing
        KubeRayOp->>CodeFlareOp as CodeFlare: Wrap in AppWrapper
        CodeFlareOp->>KueueCtrl as Kueue: Admit workload
        KueueCtrl-->>CodeFlareOp: Resources available
    end

    KubeRayOp->>RayHead as Ray Head Pod: Create head node
    KubeRayOp->>RayWorkers as Ray Worker Pods: Create worker nodes
    RayWorkers->>RayHead: Connect via Redis GCS<br/>6379/TCP

    User->>RayHead: Submit Ray job<br/>Ray client API
    RayHead->>RayWorkers: Distribute tasks
    RayWorkers->>S3: Store checkpoints<br/>HTTPS
    RayWorkers-->>User: Training complete

    Note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 4: AI Explainability with TrustyAI

    User->>Dashboard: Create TrustyAIService CR
    Dashboard->>TrustyAIOp as TrustyAI Operator: Deploy TrustyAI
    TrustyAIOp->>TrustyAISvc as TrustyAI Service: Create deployment + Route
    TrustyAIOp->>KServeCtrl: Patch InferenceService<br/>Add inference logger

    User->>Predictor: Inference request
    Predictor->>TrustyAISvc: Send payload copy<br/>Inference logger
    TrustyAISvc->>TrustyAISvc: Compute fairness metrics<br/>SPD, DIR
    TrustyAISvc->>Prometheus: Expose metrics<br/>ServiceMonitor
    Prometheus->>Dashboard: Query fairness metrics
    Dashboard-->>User: Display bias analysis
